Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:38.52,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}与其唧唧喳喳  不如do it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.84,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今天开始你也蒙面唧唧唧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:46.07,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}这个世界弱肉强食  so do it
