Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,黑川茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个高二的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了
