Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.93,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\bord2.2\be0\fsp3\fs30\c&HF9FBF8&\3c&H081E9A&\3a&H14&\1a&H14&\b0\pos(232,662)}女演员 高中二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高三的MEM啾
